high_descs: Turn around and then turn left.
Turn left and move to the spoon.
Open the spoon and bowl near the window.
Pick the spoon from the bowl.
Pick the bowl from the sink.
Place the bowl inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the spoon and bowl inside the sink basin.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Pick up the spoon from the bottom of the fridge.
Put the spoon in the bowl in the bottom shelf of the fridge.
Pick up the bowl with the spoon.
Turn around and walk to the kitchen sink.
Put the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled Bowl with the Spoon in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Open the cupboard and take the spoon & bowl which is inside it.
Head to the sink and then turn left.
Put the spoon and the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the Spoon and the Bowl in the SinkBasin.
